snippet.title: TV ROYALE | New Heroes: Wizard & Ice Golem!
snippet.description:
X â–º https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Tower Troops from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

snippet.title: AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY (2026) | Thor Trailer | Marvel Comics | Concept
snippet.description:
#Marvel #Avengers #Avengersdoomsday #ChrisEvans #Robertdowneyjr 
 
ğŸ¥ Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Avengers: Doomsday brings the Marvel Cinematic Universe into its most dangerous chapter yet as a new global threat rises. The Avengers Doomsday official trailer teases the shocking arrival of Doctor Doom, portrayed by Robert Downey Jr., setting the stage for an epic clash that will reshape the future of the MCU. Packed with multiversal stakes, iconic heroes, and dark comic-inspired themes, this Avengers 2026 movie launches Marvel Phase 6 with a powerful warning: Doomsday is coming.

The inspiration behind this video:
The Marvel Cinematic Universe is forever changed! In this video, we break down the explosive Avengers Doomsday trailer , analyzing every hidden detail in the Avengers Doomsday official trailer that just dropped. With the Avengers 2026 release date fast approaching, the hype for Avengers Doomsday is at an all-time high. We discuss how Marvel Studios has set the stage for the multiverse's darkest hour and what the footage reveals about the plot of the highly anticipated Avengers Doomsday movie . Whether you are here for the action or the lore, this is your ultimate guide to the Avengers Doomsday marvel trailer .

All eyes are on the shocking return of the king: Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom . We dive deep into the Avengers Doomsday cast and the theories surrounding the Doctor Doom MCU incarnation. Is this a twisted Tony Stark variant, or has Robert Downey Jr MCU returned as the true Victor Von Doom? We analyze the showdowns teased in the Avengers Doomsday teaser and how the remaining heroes will cope with an enemy who wears the face of their fallen friend. This isn't just an Avengers film; it looks like a full-blown Doctor Doom movie that will redefine the Marvel Cinematic Universe .

Finally, we explore the wider implications for MCU Phase 5 and the kick-off of Marvel Phase 6 . We provide a frame-by-frame analysis of the Doomsday trailer , pointing out easter eggs from the comics and connections to Secret Wars . From the visual tone of the Dr. Doom trailer moments to the updated team roster, we cover everything you need to know about the Avengers Doomsday trailer official release. Don't miss our full reaction and predictions for Avengers doctor doom and the future of Marvel .

â—–Made/Edited By Usâ——
(SFX, VFX, Art) 
â–º Art by TeaserCon IG:  /teaserconofficial
â—–Attention viewersâ—— This Film & Animation video created only for Entertainment. 
Most of VFX created by us.

Thank You So Much For Watching!

Tried to do something different, hope you guys enjoy :)

Go get the Jack Linkâ€™s x MrBeast beef sticks right now ğŸ‘‰ https://bit.ly/JLMBYT1

Massive shoutout to Ish who helped co-host this video, heâ€™s an amazing storyteller and I canâ€™t thank him enough for his time and energy, go check him out: https://youtube.com/@ish

We had thousands of players try to join our first large scale, multi day civilization event in a first come first serve basis. We accepted the first 500 boys and 500 girls who joined in chronological order on the Minecraft server when it went live. If a player broke the rules they agreed to in any way or lied on their application about any information to try and sabotage other players, they were banned by the staff who were monitoring 24/7 after an investigation, their actions were reversed and players they killed were revived, and they were replaced with the next boy or girl in line who had tried to join the server earlier in chronological order.

snippet.title: Bridgerton Season 4 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Behind the cover of a mask, anything can happen. Bridgerton Season 4 will arrive in two parts with Part 1 premiering January 29th and Part 2 on February 26th. Only on Netflix.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81511877

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Bridgerton Season 4 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

In a new tale from the ton, eternal bachelor Benedict Bridgerton finally meets his match: a captivating lady's maid in disguise at a masquerade ball.

The goal behind this project is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through original concepts that blend visual effects, sound design, and AI technologies. By combining these elements, I aim to deliver a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended purely to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. â€” In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story centers on Thor as the last surviving god in a universe steadily collapsing under Doctor Doomâ€™s dominion, where fate itself has been weaponized and divinity is declared obsolete. Stripped of Asgard, family, and certainty, Thor is no longer defined by conquest or legend but by doubt, grief, and an unfamiliar fear born from love and responsibility. As Doomâ€™s shadow looms over existence, Thor confronts the question of whether gods still have a place in a world that no longer believes in them, forcing him to reassess his worth beyond battle and thunder. The narrative reframes his destiny, not as a warrior seeking glory, but as a protector fighting to preserve what little remains, driven by faith, loss, and the resolve of a father determined to return to what he loves. The trailer builds toward an inevitable reckoning, positioning Thorâ€™s reclaimed purpose against Doomâ€™s control of time and destiny, setting a somber, emotional, and mythic foundation for the conflict to come.

snippet.title: SAG HARBOR
snippet.description:
lampin' in the hamptons
looking for estates not a mansion
scanning for the acreage in the pamphlet
i think this the big one sanford, 
and son got his fourth number one in a row i'm a champion
don't tap the glassy, i'd rather tap the pedal on the chassis
call it jasper it's blowing gassy
them boys ain't got no rhythm uptempo got em aggy
she sponging up my plankton it got her moving crabby
took the plane to martha, damn how much it cost ya?
blink and it's 182 like travis barker
but this the baby one, this the larva
easier to get from sag harbor, all bargain, all august, australia 
picked up another bag no garbage 
i'm tired if we keeping it facts
fuck work bro i need to relax
a piece of mind is what i need to get back

i'm grindin' like itâ€™s 2002
beating on the table
i'm tryna tag 100 million dollars out the label
to you that's just a fable
i'll show up with a camera and ruler just in case itâ€™s hard for them to get my angle
i'm with my nigga lionel
bluffing on an island
talking bout a village we can build, i'm feeling tribal
freedom is our destination praying that it's final
ship that car for 3mil and they forgot to send the title got damn!
the moment where your idol is your rival
i'm flying through the fire and i ain't break a sweat yet
i keep a lil water in the vial
nino brown necklace, custom made lexus
lust in my body made commitment see the exit
i pray to god i settle down and stop the second guessing
guilt from got me emotionally regressing
until then i'm pollywog leaping in affection  

i gave niggas shoulders they can cry on
i ain't like their nature so i had to switch the biome
they ain't seeing green from me 
i'm switching to an iphone
fuck who y'all calling the best
i seen their ticket sales, give it rest
they got y'all craniums hexxed
i'm on the road to doing stadiums next 
but y'all keep counting me out, what's the cheat code?
corny ass niggas still worried about a street code 
we supposed to own the ball, y'all worried bout shooting free throws 
for big dollas, dog collars, from sun dodgers
the catalyst of all the world problems
white bitches saying period at end of the sentence
but wouldn't let the black girls they copy inside their kitchen
listen, i be off the coast bro
away from these crumbs spending bread eating toast bro
backseat of the phantom

snippet.title: How I Tricked a Pokemon Tournament
snippet.description:
There is an ability that, if it ever got popular, could single handedly ruin competitive Pokemon. Fortunately, nobody thinks this ability is very good. Except... I think they're wrong. I Entered the Milwaukee Regional Championships with Hisuian Zoroark.

Check out all my Scarlet and Violet videos here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLb_5fF_O3FvjEglm1tAGgGVuJo4YTzrV4

snippet.title: Can YOU Beat EVERY FNAF Game at the SAME TIME? (7 GAMES)
snippet.description:
In this video I attempt to beat every single mainline FNAF game at the exact same time. Meaning that at the beginning of a night, we must start every game at the exact same time, dying in ANY of the games means resetting ALL of them back to the beginning of the night. 

Thank you to flairex for the SL no custom cursor mod!:
@Flairex 

If you're interested in learning more about max modes, check out the All Modes list!
All modes list: https://allmodeslist.pages.dev/
All modes list discord server: https://discord.gg/hAYSEaUApr

Raw unedited Proof: https://youtu.be/obYxinUtFi8

If you'd like to view any of the music used in this video, here's a link to the google doc that I store all of it on: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xc7efV51G56mSzWbP-Qi7l7A4lKIo-HB5eV5L4lJBqY/edit?usp=sharing

thumbnail by glennthumbnail: https://ytjobs.co/talent/profile/107568?r=469&utm_campaign=share-profile&utm_ref=talent&utm_source=copylink

Video Chapters:
0:00 - Intro / Challenge Rules
2:28 - Night 1
5:27 - Night 2
28:12 - Night 3
43:41 - Night 4
59:58 - Night 5
1:19:29 - Outro

snippet.title: Usher - DJ Got Us Fallin' In Love (Lyrics) ft. Pitbull
snippet.description:
Check out our Playlist:
https://open.spotify.com/playlist/1oJZ98sB3FbQAbrZkEbdtQ?si=_xvuL7hdQlu_oQySAWsv2A

Lyrics:
[Intro: Usher]
Usher, Usher, Usher
Yeah, man

[Verse 1: Usher]
So we back in the club
With our bodies rockin' from
Side to side, side-side to side, uh
Thank God the week is done
I feel like a zombie
Gone back to life, back-back to life
[Pre-Chorus: Usher]
Hands up, uh
Yeah, suddenly, we all got our hands up, uh
No control of my body
Ain't I seen you before?
I think I remember those eyes, eyes, eyes
Eyes, eye-eyes

[Chorus: Usher]
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (Love again)
Yeah, baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (L-love again-gain)
So dance, dance like it's the last, last night
Of your life, life, gon' get you right
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (L-love again-gain)

[Verse 2: Usher]
Keep downin' drinks like there's no tomorrow
There's just right, now, now, now
Now, now, now, now
Gon' set the roof on fire
Gonna burn this motherf***** down, down, down
Down, down, down, down (Come on)
[Pre-Chorus: Usher]
Hands up, uh
When the music drops, we both put our hands up
Put your hands on my body
Swear I've seen you before
I think I remember those eyes, eyes, eyes
Eyes, eye-eyes

[Chorus: Usher & Pitbull]
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (Love again)
Yeah, baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (L-love again-gain, oh yeah)
So dance, dance like it's the last, last night
Of your life, life, gon' get you right
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (L-love again-gain Usher, don't lie! haha, ohh)

[Verse 3: Pitbull]
Hear no evil, I speak no evil, I see no evil
Get it, baby, hope you catch that like T.O
That's how we roll
My life is a movie and you just TiVo, ha
Mami got me twisted like a dreadlock
She don't wrestle, but I got her in a headlock
Yabba-dabba-doo, make her bed rock
Mami on fire, pshh, red hot
Bada bing, bada boom
Mr. Worldwide as I step in the room
I'm a hustler, baby, but that you knew
And tonight it's just me and you, dale
[Chorus: Usher & Pitbull]
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again
(Mr. Worldwide, yeah, yeah, let's take over the world, haha)
Yeah, baby, tonight (Hahahaha, yeah man)
The DJ got us falling in love, falling in love, o-oh
(Dale) (Let go)
So dance, dance like it's the last, last night
Of your life, life, gon' get you right (Woo!)
(Come on, come on)
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again
Yeah (Love again)
Yeah, baby, tonight
(Yeah, somebody get the DJ's up, somebody get the DJ's up)
The DJ got us falling in love again (L-love again-gain)
(Somebody get the hands up, get the hands up, get your hands up, aw, come on)
So dance, dance like it's the last, last night
Of your life, life, Gon' get you right
'Cause baby, tonight
The DJ got us falling in love again (L-love again-gain)

[Outro: Usher & Pitbull]
Hahaha...
Yeah
Thank you, DJ, haha

#Usher #Pitbull #DJGotUsFallinInLove #lyrics

Meliput Teaser Tampilan Pertama Spider-Man Brand New Day, Bruce Banner sebagai Hulk yang Liar, Karakter Baru Sadie Sink, Spider-Man vs Punisher. Reuni Tom Holland dan Jon Bernthal. Tampilan Pertama Kostum Spider-Man Baru. Pengumuman Hulk. Mengapa Bruce Banner akan membantu Spider-Man, Spider-Man vs Hulk, Referensi sebelumnya tentang Hulk dalam Film Spider-Man. Crossover Aksi Langsung Stan Lee Incredible Hulk dan Spider-Man di tahun 1980-an. Scorpion Kembali, Tombstone, penjahat baru lainnya.

Penjelasan Spider-Man Brand New Day. Penjahat Baru, Perubahan Spider-Man Tom Holland, Koneksi Trailer Avengers Doomsday. Karakter Baru, Kostum Spider-Man Baru. Trailer Spider-Man Beyond The Spider-Verse. Trailer Spider-Man Noir, Koneksi Sadie Sink dan Tobey Maguire sebagai Spider-Man.

Trailer Avengers Doomsday. Robert Downey Jr. sebagai Doctor Doom, Black Panther Baru, X-Men, Doctor Strange, Cuplikan Pertama Avengers Secret Wars, Battleworld MCU. Fantastic Four, Franklin Richards. Ian McKellen sebagai Magneto, Patrick Stewart sebagai Professor X, Kesley Grammer sebagai Beast, Thor Kembali, Mystique, Cyclops, Nightcrawler, X-Men Asli.

Easter Egg Deadpool dan Wolverine. Mengapa Marvel melakukan reboot MCU dengan Avengers 6 Secret Wars. Apa yang akan berubah dengan semua Avengers, Iron Man Baru, X-Men, Mutan seperti Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man, dan karakter lainnya. Masih banyak lagi trailer Marvel yang akan datang, termasuk trailer Avengers Doomsday, dan video Spider-Man Brand New Day lainnya yang akan segera hadir!

Video episode Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2 saya akan diunggah selanjutnya. Selamat Natal!

snippet.title: John Denver - Take Me Home, Country Roads (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
John Denver - Take Me Home, Country Roads (Lyrics)

Follow John Denver:
https://www.instagram.com/johndenvermusic/
https://www.facebook.com/JohnDenver/
https://twitter.com/JohnDenverMusic

Lyrics:

[Verse 1]
Almost Heaven, West Virginia
Blue Ridge Mountains, Shenandoah River
Life is old there, older than the trees
Younger than the mountains, growing like a breeze

[Chorus]
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads

[Verse 2]
All my memories gather 'round her
Miner's lady, stranger to blue water
Dark and dusty, painted on the sky
Misty taste of moonshine, teardrop in my eye

[Chorus]
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads

[Bridge]
I hear her voice in the morning hour, she calls me
The radio reminds me of my home far away
Driving down the road, I get a feeling
That I should have been home yesterday, yesterday

[Chorus]
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads
Country roads, take me home
To the place I belong
West Virginia, mountain mama
Take me home, country roads

[Outro]
Take me home, (Down) country roads
Take me home, (Down) country roads

People Wanted a Dino Park, I Gave Them an Extinction-Level Event - Jurassic World Evolution 3 - Let's Game It Out

----------

Check it out on Steam â–º https://store.steampowered.com/app/2958130/Jurassic_World_Evolution_3/

More about Jurassic World Evolution 3 (from Steam):

The next entry in the award-winning series, Jurassic World Evolution 3 puts you in control of building and running your very own Jurassic World.

Help life find a way by synthesising, breeding, and nurturing prehistoric species. Manage each species and allow them to thrive, while helping your dinosaurs raise families and pass their genes onto future generations.

Create incredible havens for your dinosaurs to help them flourish, build exciting new attractions to amaze guests, and maintain control when disaster inevitably strikes.

With over 85 awe-inspiring pre-historic species, 75 of which allow you to manage, breed and nurture families of dinosaurs across entire generations. Rear them from playful juveniles into awe-inspiring adults, each with distinct female, male, and juvenile variants.

Park guests will marvel as these majestic creatures socialise and react to the vibrant world around them.

Manage unique social needs and observe brand new behaviours, with semi-aquatic dinosaurs venturing into deep water and pterosaurs walking on land.

Create jaw-dropping parks with new creative tools never before seen in the Jurassic World Evolution series! From groundbreaking terrain editing to modular scenery customisation â€“ build and tweak every aspect of your park from the ground up or, generate a custom map which is unique every time with the Island Generator. The choice is in your hands!

Build your sites with naturalistic enclosures using steep slopes and scenery, introduce stunning new attractions such as the Balloon Tour, a close-up attraction that let guests see and touch prehistoric animals with the Dinosaur Encounter or the iconic Cretaceous Cruise where guests can view dinosaurs from a new watery perspective!â€¯â€¯ 

Create, upload and share cross-platform community creations using the Frontier Workshop. Browse the very best creations from the community, place them in your own game or craft your own custom parks, buildings and enclosures before sharing for other players to use.

Join familiar faces from the Jurassic franchise, including Dr. Ian Malcolm (voiced by Jeff Goldblum) and embark on a non-linear campaign across a sprawling world map filled with iconic locations such as the Montana Badlands, and new locations such as Japanâ€”each offering thrilling new challenges. Every decision will test your park management skills as you balance competing human interests with the delicate integration of dinosaurs into a modern world.

Youâ€™ll need to juggle your reputation with three influential industry sectors and the unique demands of an array of site-owning clients. But be warned: not everyone wants to see the dinosaurs thrive.

Set your site up to run as efficiently as possible with powerful and accessible park management tools provide control over your parkâ€™s operations.

But chaos is the only certainty, so prepare for disaster using new security cameras that will help automate the response to escaped dinosaurs and deploy your Maintenance team to keep threats contained by delivering critical repairs across the site.

Manage unique social needs and observe brand new behaviours, with semi-aquatic dinosaurs venturing into deep water and pterosaurs walking on land.

Create jaw-dropping parks with new creative tools never before seen in the Jurassic World Evolution series! From groundbreaking terrain editing to modular scenery customisation â€“ build and tweak every aspect of your park from the ground up or, generate a custom map which is unique every time with the Island Generator. The choice is in your hands!

Build your sites with naturalistic enclosures using steep slopes and scenery, introduce stunning new attractions such as the Balloon Tour, a close-up attraction that let guests see and touch prehistoric animals with the Dinosaur Encounter or the iconic Cretaceous Cruise where guests can view dinosaurs from a new watery perspective!â€¯â€¯ 

Create, upload and share cross-platform community creations using the Frontier Workshop. Browse the very best creations from the community, place them in your own game or craft your own custom parks, buildings and enclosures before sharing for other players to use.

Join familiar faces from the Jurassic franchise, including Dr. Ian Malcolm (voiced by Jeff Goldblum) and embark on a non-linear campaign across a sprawling world map filled with iconic locations such as the Montana Badlands, and new locations such as Japanâ€”each offering thrilling new challenges. Every decision will test your park management skills as you balance competing human interests with the delicate integration of dinosaurs into a modern world.

Youâ€™ll need to juggle your reputation with three influential industry sectors and the unique demands of an array of site-owning clients. But be warned: not everyone wants to see the dinosaurs thrive.

Set your site up to run as efficiently as possible with powerful and accessible park management tools provide control over your parkâ€™s operations.

But chaos is the only certainty, so prepare for disaster using new security cameras that will help automate the response to escaped dinosaurs and deploy your Maintenance team to keep threats contained by delivering critical repairs across the site.

snippet.title: Can The Spiffing Brit Beat EU5 As A Tiny Island - Europa Universalis 5 Is A Perfectly Balanced Game
snippet.description:
Welcome to the greatest game of all time! Or at least it is if you look at the amount of hours I have added to my steam account in the last few weeks. I am of course talking about Europa Universalis V! So what is EU5, rather simply this game is a 4X grand strategy game set between 5 centuries of human history starting in the late medieval leading into things like the renaissance and era of exploration filled with colonisation and discovery. Paradox on steam describe the game as so: Use war, trade or diplomacy to satisfy your grandest ambitions and dominate five centuries of history in the newest version of Europa Universalis, Paradox Interactive's flagship historical grand strategy game.

I think its a pretty darn accurate representation of the game as trade war and diplomacy make up the foundational pillars of this strategy game. However today I am not intending to play the game in a way that was intended. 

You Can Purchase the game here: https://paradoxinteractive.i38e.net/6y4ovq
(Use code "Spiffing" At checkout)
(Might be cheaper than steam in your local currency)

He slid into the chair, camera rolling, heart pounding. The screen shimmered as he purchased the bonus outright. Instantly, the casino noise faded into a low hum as animated symbols exploded across the reels. The first spin landed hardâ€”multipliers flashing, coins clinkingâ€”but the payout barely moved the meter. Brettski frowned. Spin two was worse. Dead symbols. No upgrades. No hope.

Chat began to panic.

Spin three teased him. A rare symbol dropped in the center reel, glowing brighter than anything heâ€™d seen. The machine slowed, almost breathing. The potential win counter flickered, jumpedâ€¦ then froze. The symbol shattered into dust. Minimum hit.

â€œOkay,â€ Brettski muttered, forcing a grin. â€œItâ€™s warming up.â€

Then everything changed.

Spin four triggered a hidden mechanicâ€”one the slot hadnâ€™t shown in its preview. The screen cracked open, revealing a shadow bonus inside the bonus. The lights around the machine dimmed. Even nearby players leaned in. Multipliers stacked. Wilds locked. The win counter started climbing fastâ€¦ then fasterâ€¦ then faster still.

Brettski shot out of his seat.

But before the reels could finish, the machine stuttered. The screen went black. A casino attendant started walking over. The counter stopped mid-jump, frozen on a number that couldâ€™ve been life-changingâ€”or nothing at all.

The machine rebooted.

When the screen came back on, a single message blinked in red:

**â€œBONUS STATE ERROR â€” RESUME OR VOID?â€**

Brettski stared at the screen, finger hovering over the button, knowing whatever he chose next would decide whether this $5,000 bonus buy became the greatest win of his lifeâ€¦ or his most brutal loss yet.

snippet.title: Getting Every Badge in Robloxâ€™s Weirdest Puzzle Game
snippet.description:
In this video, I got every badge in Roblox's weirdest puzzle game, called 'a dream you've had before'. This challenge was much more difficult than I expected, as while the game looks simple on the surface, it hides insanely hard challenges, and this ended up being the hardest thing I have done in a video game so far.

FOLLOW ME ON STUFF
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/lilykdk
Twitter: https://x.com/valkshotyuri

A dream you've had before is an awesome Roblox game developed by 4slug, if you're watching this video and you haven't played it yet, I highly suggest you do, as it's a really fun experience.

Every song I used in Chronological Order
https://rentry.co/lilymusic

Gunakan Kode Bintang KLOUDZ untuk mendukung saya saat membeli Robux (tanpa biaya tambahan untuk Anda)

Ikuti saya di Twitter - https://twitter.com/kalis_jaden

Gabung ke Discord! - https://discord.gg/kloudz

Apa itu Roblox?

Roblox adalah platform global tempat jutaan orang berkumpul setiap hari untuk membayangkan, menciptakan, dan berbagi pengalaman satu sama lain di dunia 3D imersif yang dibuat oleh pengguna.

Jenis permainan di Roblox sama tak terbatasnya dengan imajinasi para kreator itu sendiri.

snippet.title: Is This Seat Taken? First Look!
snippet.description:
Is This Seat Taken? is a 2025 puzzle video game developed by Poti Poti Studio and published by Wholesome Games. 

Donations are 100% Optional and Never Donate More Than You Can Afford Please: https://streamlabs.com/beaconofnick/tip

Rules For The Chat: 
 1. Be Respectful to Mods and Everyone
 2. Please keep the chat PG
 3. No Self Promo
 4. No Spamming the chat
 5. No Spoilers about this game, Scarlet and Violet or about new movies/shows
6. Moderators are essentially extensions of myself. Please listen to them.
7.You must flip a pancake IRL every time Nick gets Splatted in Splatoon or gets a shiny (This one is a joke)
8. I say this with love but please no complaining if your messages get ignored at any point. I am one guy trying to stream and read chat and I will not encourage that type of behavior. 

Music by: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3jXokTqt0bc&t=882s

Chat Commands for Links: 
!discord
!fc for friendcode
!instagram 
!twitter
!pogo

snippet.title: I was LATE To SCHOOL in Roblox...
snippet.description:
I failed a ROBLOX IQ Test... AGAIN
Like and Subscribe for more! 

Yes this is Lia and this is my new gaming channel Liabloxi where I will be uploading Roblox gaming videos

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Ya, ini Lia dan ini adalah saluran game baruku, Liabloxi, tempat aku akan mengunggah video game Roblox.

Apa itu Roblox? ROBLOX adalah taman bermain dan bengkel virtual online, tempat anak-anak dari segala usia dapat berinteraksi, berkreasi, bersenang-senang, dan belajar dengan aman. Keunikannya terletak pada hampir semua hal di ROBLOX dirancang dan dibangun oleh anggota komunitas. ROBLOX dirancang untuk usia 13 hingga 18 tahun, tetapi terbuka untuk semua usia. Setiap pemain memulai dengan memilih avatar dan memberinya identitas. Mereka kemudian dapat menjelajahi ROBLOX â€” berinteraksi dengan orang lain melalui obrolan, bermain game, atau berkolaborasi dalam proyek kreatif. Setiap pemain juga diberikan sebidang lahan virtual yang belum dikembangkan beserta kotak peralatan virtual untuk mendesain dan membangun apa pun â€” baik itu gedung pencakar langit yang dapat dilalui, helikopter yang berfungsi, mesin pinball raksasa, permainan "Capture the Flag" multipemain, atau kreasi lain yang belum terbayangkan. Tidak ada biaya untuk lahan virtual pertama ini. Dengan berpartisipasi dan membangun hal-hal keren, anggota ROBLOX dapat memperoleh lencana khusus serta mata uang ROBLOX ("Robux"). Sebagai gantinya, mereka dapat berbelanja di katalog online untuk membeli pakaian dan aksesori avatar serta bahan bangunan premium, komponen interaktif, dan mekanisme yang berfungsi.

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Met deze Robux kunnen ze vervolgens in de online catalogus winkelen om kleding en accessoires voor hun avatar te kopen, evenals hoogwaardige bouwmaterialen, interactieve componenten en werkende mechanismen.
